    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you should expect some minor oil seeps and a suspension that feels a bit loose over bumps. Cosmetically, the exterior has several noticeable scratches, paint fading on the hood, and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. It is a solid candidate for someone willing to put in a little work to bring it back to its best or for those needing an affordable, functional car as-is.",
