    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. It exhibits a refined aesthetic paired with a documented history of mechanical care, ensuring continued reliability and peak performance. The interior remains composed and functional, reflecting a standard of ownership that prioritizes both longevity and comfort. An ideal acquisition for those seeking an executive-level driving experience without the premium of a showroom-new price point.",
