    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride. It's been such a reliable companion for me and still runs like a dream. It's in really solid shape\u2014well-taken care of and ready for its next adventure! If you're looking for something dependable that still looks great on the road, this is the one. I've loved driving this car and I'm sure you will too. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 32500.0,
