    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six engine. This specimen boasts a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission delivering power to the rear wheels via a factory M-Variable differential lock. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and subframe reinforcement, ensuring the structural integrity of the chassis under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its communicative feedback with upgraded bushings, while the individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous throttle response up to the 8,000 RPM redline. While showing signs of careful use consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals remain robust, offering a pure analog driving experience for the discerning pilot.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 48
    },
    {
